data.description:
This nearly 4,000 sq ft two owner home has so many surprises and a great deal of potential. Located in a beautiful Golf Course community,
this home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, bonus room, office/study, a large kitchen, hearth room, 2 living spaces, dining room and breakfast. You will find 5
fireplaces throughout and a huge deck and an upper level balcony. There is also a partially finished bonus room and a secret room. It needs work
but is in move in condition.
